snippet.title: HUNT3R OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Romance game but with turn-based battles and your only romance option is a cyborg.  Story shamelessly inspired by Stella/Elle's interactions in Starcrash, a really crappy movie but with great human + robot  shipping fuel.

AVAILABLE ON ITCH.IO ON JUNE 30TH 2022: https://drone-garden-studios.itch.io/hunt3r
